title: S12 Ep91: Lucifer: Origins & Revelations
itunes:title: Lucifer: Origins & Revelations
description:
Today our guest, Priscilla Vogelbacher raises the question, Is the Church and current Religion hiding a dark truth about the origins of Lucifer? Is the truth more frightening than anything we have been led to believe?
We will look into her new book and discuss the highly controversial subject of Lucifer and what she believes his "real" story may reveal.
